<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_security_acl"><sys_security_acl action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><admin_overrides>true</admin_overrides><advanced>true</advanced><condition/><description>Allow write for file_name in sys_attachment, if the ACL script returns true. (v1.2)</description><name>sys_attachment.file_name</name><operation display_value="write">write</operation><script><![CDATA[answer = canEditFileName();

function canEditFileName() {
	var tableName = current.getValue("table_name");
	var parentRecord = new GlideRecord(tableName);
	
	if (parentRecord.get(current.getValue("table_sys_id")))
		return parentRecord.canWrite();
	
	return false;
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_security_acl</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>andrew.pishchulin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2020-03-09 21:35:28</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>c1069e48db6748100abfd1b1ca9619ed</sys_id><sys_mod_count>2</sys_mod_count><sys_name>sys_attachment.file_name</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_security_acl_c1069e48db6748100abfd1b1ca9619ed</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>andrew.pishchulin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2021-01-13 22:57:01</sys_updated_on><type display_value="record">record</type></sys_security_acl></record_update>
